<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/high-speed-two-limited> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "High Speed Two (HS2) Limited is the company responsible for developing and promoting the UK’s new high speed rail network. It is funded by grant-in-aid from the government. HS2 Ltd is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Department for Transport ."@en .
